## ❗ Challenge Faced & Resolution

### Issue: Nginx Configuration Error

During setup, Nginx failed to start due to:

> `"location directive is not allowed here"`

### Root Cause:

A `location` block was placed outside the `server` context in the Nginx configuration file.

### Fix:

* Corrected brace structure
* Ensured all directives (`location`, `include`, `error_page`) were inside the `server` block
* Validated configuration using `nginx -t` before restart

